<h1>Welcome to ExIndex</h1>
<p>
 ExIndex is an index processor based on the experiences of makeindex and Xindy.
 As a consequences ExIndex can be used instead of makeindex and Xindy.
</p>
<p>
 ExIndex is a re-implementation. As such ExIndex contains some extensions to
 Xindy and Makeindex. Details can be found in the documentation.
</p>

<h1>Homepage</h1>
<p>
 ExIndex has been developed in the context of the ExTeX project.
 ExTeX is present on the Web. On the Homepage you can find additional
 information:
</p>
<p>
 <a href="http://www.extex.org">http://www.extex.org</a>
